{"tid":928054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界妓廠 最大雞隻輸出國]新加坡警方破獲賣淫集團! 其中144名妓女來自中國!","createTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T22:04:26.000Z","uid":179810,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"278409aa5b9fc536fb9d85d5c3dd02c58f364616","tid":928054,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/04/XN3geF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2FXN3geF.jpg&h=70bf8695&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/04/BSz3K8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2FBSz3K8.jpg&h=824371b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/04/pSRzh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2FpSRzh8.jpg&h=00ead54a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n12月3日中國與新加坡警方展開聯合行動，成功摧毀一個誘騙中國婦女赴新加坡賣淫的犯罪組織，共抓獲嫌疑人30名及賣淫婦女144人。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2018年3月，中方接新加坡警方通報，在偵查拐賣人口案時，發現犯罪團伙通過微信等誘騙上百名中國婦女到新加坡賣淫。公安部對此高度重視，立即循線追蹤。經初步偵查，發現周某勝(綽號「君子」，男，27歲，江蘇連雲港人)、朱某豪(男，27歲，江蘇連雲港人)為首的組織安排婦女到新加坡賣淫。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n11月22日，中國和新加坡警方聯合行動，查明周某勝、朱某豪為首的犯罪集團與新加坡境內不法分子相互勾聯，以出國打工、高薪收入為誘餌，誘騙中國婦女赴新加坡招嫖賣淫.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181203/mobile/bkn-20181203200523844-1203_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181203%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181203200523844-1203_00952_001.html&d=PVI6hBKaofi%2BzSQIbQ7rMP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b4dd8fa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181203/mobile/bkn-20181203200523844-1203_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"de03523b6729baa601624d4454e628b0939ee99f","tid":928054,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"妓女強國，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c727341619331b8495c57867cf2def7c9c64113","tid":928054,"uid":61280,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:41:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">女支，妓也！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"51c01eceb8daacbcad07318c6030394dad923a4f","tid":928054,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:48:39.000Z","msg":"江蘇省去新加坡省搵食 有問題嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32250282f0808c5849d510b602d7049a9c254587","tid":928054,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T19:23:57.000Z","msg":"誘騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be44fb85eeb9953a55426b0d0790ba9d5874f364","tid":928054,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:31:12.000Z","msg":"準備屎忽開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bdc0e7cd3eb9314ffd523180635089593abbd0","tid":928054,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be44fb85eeb9953a55426b0d0790ba9d5874f364","tid":928054,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:31:12.000Z","msg":"準備屎忽開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:32:53.000Z","msg":"我柒左, 原來大陸拉到, 咁都好d, 俾錢搞返出黎<br />\n屎忽仲好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bebc92e788bb8c6a53b89e1a8fa2998a3aed54","tid":928054,"uid":5